###############################################################
# ERROR CASES — useful for testing auth middleware
###############################################################

### No token (should return 401)
GET {{gateway}}/api/notes

###

### Invalid token (should return 401)
GET {{gateway}}/api/notes
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### Non-existent note (should return 404)
GET {{gateway}}/api/notes/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Invalid ObjectId format (should return 400)
GET {{gateway}}/api/notes/not-a-valid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
